# 🛗 Event-Driven Elevator Simulator

A professional Windows Forms-based elevator control system demonstrating event-driven architecture in C# .NET. **Now with realistic apartment/hotel elevator behavior and correct floor visualization!**

## Features

✅ **3-Floor Elevator System (Real-World Accurate)**
- Ground Floor (Floor 1) - at BOTTOM
- Floor 2 - in MIDDLE
- Floor 3 - at TOP
- Just like real apartment/hotel elevators!

✅ **Event-Driven Architecture**
- Clean separation of concerns using C# events
- Non-blocking asynchronous operations
- Real-time event logging

✅ **Realistic Elevator Behavior**
- Moves smoothly between floors
- Intelligent request queuing
- Automatic direction management (Up/Down/Idle)
- Door open/close animation (2 seconds each)
- 2 seconds per floor movement
- Multiple request handling

✅ **Professional UI Design**
- Visual elevator cars with opening/closing doors
- Control panel with floor buttons
- Digital floor display (cyan text)
- Comprehensive event log with timestamps
- Realistic door animation and handles

