## Real-World Behavior ✨

This elevator behaves exactly like elevators in apartments and hotels:

- ✅ Floors are correctly positioned (1 at bottom, 3 at top)
- ✅ Elevator car moves between floors smoothly
- ✅ Door opens when reaching requested floor
- ✅ Door stays open for passenger entry/exit
- ✅ Door closes and continues to next request
- ✅ Handles multiple requests intelligently
- ✅ Changes direction when needed

## Events Fired

The elevator system fires the following events:

- **FloorChanged**: When elevator reaches a new floor
- **DirectionChanged**: When elevator changes direction (Up/Down/Idle)
- **RequestAdded**: When a floor is requested
- **DoorsOpened**: When doors open at a floor
- **DoorsClosed**: When doors close to continue
- **ElevatorStopped**: When all requests are completed

