## Example Usage

```csharp
// Create elevator instance
var elevator = new Elevator(3);

// Subscribe to events
elevator.FloorChanged += (sender, e) => 
	Console.WriteLine($"Reached floor {e.CurrentFloor}");

// Request a floor
elevator.RequestFloor(2);
```

